  "title": "COMMAND CENTRE (CONTROLLER)",
  "description": "<h2><strong>📢 JOB VACANCY: COMMAND CENTRE CONTROLLER</strong></h2><p>📍 <strong>Work Location:</strong> Uniforce Security (Command Centre)<br />📅 <strong>Start Date:</strong> Immediate</p><h3><strong>Position Details</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Rank:</strong> <strong>Senior Security Officer (SSO)</strong></li><li><strong>Shift:</strong> <strong>Night Shift</strong><br />🕙 <strong>10:00 PM – 10:00 AM</strong></li><li><strong>Off Days:</strong> <strong>6 off-days per month</strong></li></ul><h3><strong>Key Requirements</strong></h3><p>✅ Proficient in <strong>Microsoft Office</strong> (especially <strong>Excel</strong>)<br />✅ Experienced in <strong>rostering planning and manpower scheduling using Excel</strong><br />✅ <strong>Customer service–oriented</strong> with good communication skills<br />✅ Able to work independently in a <strong>Command Centre environment</strong><br />✅ Alert, responsible, and detail-oriented</p><h3><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Monitor CCTV systems and alarm panels.</li><li>Perform <strong>rostering planning, duty scheduling, and manpower tracking using Excel.</strong></li><li>Coordinate deployment with ground officers and supervisors.</li><li>Log incidents and prepare accurate reports.</li><li>Handle calls and provide professional customer service.</li><li>Ensure security operations comply with SOPs.</li></ul><p>📞 <strong>Interested applicants, whatsapp HR +65 9643 2402 for more information or to apply.</strong></p>",
