    "description": "<p>Uniforce Security Services Pte Ltd is backed up with combined 30 years of experience, specializing in a whole range of professional security services. We always surpass our aims through delivering workable solutions to the continual delight of our partners as the aspect of security is extremely important to our daily way of living, premises and assets.</p>  <p>Technology and the world change rapidly, and great emphasis is placed on staying ahead of the changes with a combination of the latest and modern precedence of security knowledge.</p>  <p>We are experienced in providing services in the industrial areas, commercial buildings, shopping malls, schools and residential properties. Our security personnel are well disciplined contended, properly trained and responsible.</p> ",
